  <brief_title>Patent Ductus Arteriosus (PDA) Screening Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of Serial Echocardiography to Detect an Asymptomatic Patent Ductus Arteriosus (PDA) in Very Low Birth Weight (VLBW) Infants: A Pilot Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
